because you are.

1700
01:34:13,375 --> 01:34:15,125
- Dave.
- Please sit, Mr. Dellinger.

1701
01:34:15,208 --> 01:34:17,666
- If we're guilty, why not give us a trial?
- [Leonard] Dave.

1702
01:34:17,750 --> 01:34:19,375
