1778
01:38:27,416 --> 01:38:29,125
[John] The giant turned out to be nice.

1779
01:38:29,208 --> 01:38:31,208
- [Jerry] Are you sure?
- No.

1780
01:38:31,291 --> 01:38:33,916
It's hard to believe the seven of us
weren't able to end a war.

1781
01:38:34,000 --> 01:38:35,125
