six policemen start to go after the man…

1836
01:41:05,458 --> 01:41:08,083
Sorry, the kid
who was climbing the flagpole?

1837
01:41:08,166 --> 01:41:09,416
- Yes.
- [Bill] It was dark.

1838
01:41:09,500 --> 01:41:12,666
